text: Gnathoenia bialbata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fairmaire in 1891.BioLib.cz - Gnathoenia bialbata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. It contains the varietas Gnathoenia bialbata var. latefasciata. ==References== Category:Ceroplesini Category:Beetles described in 1891
